<Layout title="Agora MeydanÄ± | Agora Go Akademisi">
  <div class="forum-container">
    
    <header class="forum-header">
      <h1>Agora MeydanÄ± ğŸ›ï¸</h1>
      <p>Toplulukla tartÄ±ÅŸ, soru sor ve fikirlerini paylaÅŸ.</p>
